---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import CodeBlock from '../../components/CodeBlock.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Performance Tuning — gpulse"
  description="Optimize gpulse for different workloads with monitoring interval tuning, history size, database settings, leak detection sensitivity, and scenario-based configurations."
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Performance Tuning</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed">
    Optimize gpulse for your workload and system configuration with these tuning recommendations.
  </p>

  <!-- Performance Goals -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">Performance Goals</h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-muted">gpulse is designed to meet these targets:</p>
  <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border bg-surface">
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Metric</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Target</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-border">
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">GPU Overhead</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">&lt; 1% impact on GPU workloads</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Memory Usage</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">&lt; 50 MB (single GPU), &lt; 150 MB (32 GPUs)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Response Time</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">&lt; 2s for CLI commands, &lt; 100ms for analysis</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Reliability</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">99.9% uptime in daemon mode</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Monitoring Interval -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">Monitoring Interval Tuning</h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
    The monitoring interval is the most impactful performance setting.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[monitoring]
# Default: 30 seconds
# Low overhead: 60-120 seconds
# High frequency: 5-15 seconds
interval-seconds = 30`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <div class="mt-6 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border bg-surface">
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Scenario</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Interval</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">CPU Impact</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-border">
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Development / Testing</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">5-10 seconds</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">~3-5%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Production (normal)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">30-60 seconds</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">~1-2%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Production (low-impact)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">120 seconds</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">&lt; 1%</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- History Size -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">History Size</h2>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[monitoring]
# Default: 1000 snapshots
# Low memory: 500
# Extended analysis: 2000-5000
history-size = 1000`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <div class="mt-6 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border bg-surface">
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">GPU Count</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Recommended Snapshots</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">RAM Impact</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-border">
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Single GPU</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">1000-2000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">~20-40 MB</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">4-8 GPUs</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">500-1000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">~10-20 MB</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">16+ GPUs</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">300-500</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">~6-10 MB</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">Memory-constrained</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">200-300</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted">~4-6 MB</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Database Performance -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">Database Performance</h2>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Enable WAL Mode</h3>
  <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Write-Ahead Logging significantly improves concurrent access — 2-3x write throughput and reduced lock contention.</p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[storage]
wal-mode = true`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Cache Size</h3>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[storage]
# Default: 20000 KB (20 MB)
# High throughput: 50000-100000 KB
# Memory-constrained: 10000 KB
cache-size-kb = 20000`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Database Location</h3>
  <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Place the database on fast storage for best results.</p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[storage]
# NVMe SSD recommended; avoid HDD
database-path = "/fast/ssd/gpu_monitoring.db"`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <!-- Leak Detection Optimization -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">Leak Detection Tuning</h2>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Minimum Samples</h3>
  <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
    Fewer samples means faster detection but more false positives. More samples means slower but more accurate detection.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[detection]
# Fast detection: 10-15
# Balanced (default): 20
# Accurate: 30-50
minimum-samples = 20`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Analysis Window</h3>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[detection]
# Quick detection: 0.5 hours
# Default: 1.0 hours
# Conservative: 2-4 hours
analysis-window-hours = 1.0`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <!-- Scenario-Based Tuning -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">Scenario-Based Configurations</h2>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Development Environment</h3>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Goal: Quick feedback, maximum detail</p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[monitoring]
interval-seconds = 5
history-size = 2000
enable-process-attribution = true

[detection]
minimum-samples = 15
confidence-threshold = 0.7
analysis-window-hours = 0.5`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Production ML Training</h3>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Goal: Minimal overhead, accurate long-term detection</p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[monitoring]
interval-seconds = 120
history-size = 500
enable-process-attribution = false

[detection]
minimum-samples = 30
confidence-threshold = 0.85
analysis-window-hours = 4.0

[storage]
wal-mode = true
cache-size-kb = 50000`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Multi-GPU Server (32 GPUs)</h3>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Goal: Monitor many GPUs efficiently</p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[monitoring]
interval-seconds = 60
history-size = 300
enable-process-attribution = false
batch-insert-size = 1000

[storage]
wal-mode = true
cache-size-kb = 100000
connection-pool-size = 50

[detection]
minimum-samples = 50
analysis-window-hours = 12.0`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">Real-Time Leak Detection</h3>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Goal: Fastest possible leak detection</p>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <CodeBlock code={`[monitoring]
interval-seconds = 5
history-size = 5000
enable-process-attribution = true

[detection]
minimum-samples = 10
confidence-threshold = 0.7
analysis-window-hours = 0.25
enable-multiple-strategies = true

[storage]
wal-mode = true
cache-size-kb = 100000`} language="toml" />
  </div>

  <!-- Best Practices -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">Best Practices</h2>
  <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-muted list-decimal list-inside">
    <li><strong>Start with defaults</strong> — tune only when needed</li>
    <li><strong>Monitor before and after</strong> — measure the impact of each change</li>
    <li><strong>Tune one parameter at a time</strong> — isolate effects</li>
    <li><strong>Document changes</strong> — track what you changed and why</li>
    <li><strong>Test under load</strong> — verify performance under realistic conditions</li>
    <li><strong>Use profiling tools</strong> — don't guess, measure</li>
    <li><strong>Review regularly</strong> — performance needs change over time</li>
  </ol>

  <!-- Troubleshooting -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold">Troubleshooting</h2>

  <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold">High CPU Usage</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
        Increase <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">interval-seconds</code>, disable <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">enable-process-attribution</code>, or reduce <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">history-size</code>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold">High Memory Usage</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
        Reduce <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">history-size</code>, enable <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">snapshot-retention-days</code>, or reduce <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">cache-size-kb</code>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold">Slow Database Queries</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
        Enable WAL mode, run <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">VACUUM</code>, increase <code class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan bg-dark px-1 py-0.5 rounded">cache-size-kb</code>, or apply retention policies.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
